  <stage stageid="91e7920a-5a64-4699-8568-036d443e4abf" name="Get Transactional Data" type="Action">
    <subsheetid>31c441e5-a950-4cbc-8527-3d935e019f7c</subsheetid>
    <narrative>
    </narrative>
    <displayx>30</displayx>
    <displayy>45</displayy>
    <displaywidth>120</displaywidth>
    <displayheight>30</displayheight>
    <font family="Tahoma" size="10" style="Regular" color="000000"/>
    <inputs>
      <input type="datetime" name="Start Date/Time" narrative="The UTC date/time from which activity counts should be retrieved. This is inclusive" expr="[Start Date]"/>
      <input type="datetime" name="End Date/Time" narrative="The UTC date/time up to and including which activity counts should be retrieved. This is inclusive. If empty, this will take all activity counts up until now." expr=""/>
      <input type="flag" name="Count item creations" narrative="True to count the work queue items being created - default is False" expr="True"/>
      <input type="flag" name="Count item locks" narrative="True to count the work queue items being locked - default is False" expr="True"/>
      <input type="flag" name="Count item deferrals" narrative="True to count the work queue items being deferred - default is False" expr="True"/>
      <input type="flag" name="Count item completions" narrative="True to count the work queue items being completed successfully - default is False" expr="True"/>
      <input type="flag" name="Count item exceptions with automatic retry" narrative="True to count the work queue items being marked with an exception and automatically retried - default is False" expr="True"/>
      <input type="flag" name="Count item exceptions without automatic retry" narrative="True to count the work queue items being marked with an exception and without an automatic retry being create - default is False" expr="True"/>
      <input type="flag" name="Count item deletions" narrative="True to count the work queue items being deleted - default is False" expr="True"/>
      <input type="flag" name="Count item forced retries" narrative="True to count the work queue items which were force retried - ie. they had been marked with an exception with no automatic retry, and had later been manually retried" expr="True"/>
      <input type="collection" name="Excluded Queue Names" narrative="The names of the queues to retrieve the activity counts for. The names should be in a column within the collection named 'Queue Name'. If any queue names do not match a queue on the system, they are ignored." expr="[Excluded Queues]"/>
    </inputs>
    <outputs>
      <output type="number" name="Created" narrative="The number of item creations counted, zero if they were not counted" stage="Created"/>
      <output type="number" name="Locked" narrative="The number of item locks counted, zero if they were not counted" stage="Locked"/>
      <output type="number" name="Deferred" narrative="The number of defferals counted, zero if they were not counted" stage="Deferred"/>
      <output type="number" name="Completed" narrative="The number of item completions counted, zero if they were not counted" stage="Completed"/>
      <output type="number" name="Exceptions with retry" narrative="The number of item exceptions with automatic retry counted, zero if they were not counted" stage="Exceptions with retry"/>
      <output type="number" name="Exceptions with no retry" narrative="The number of item exceptions without automatic retry counted, zero if they were not counted" stage="Exceptions with no retry"/>
      <output type="number" name="Deletions" narrative="The number of item deletions counted, zero if they were not counted" stage="Deletions"/>
      <output type="number" name="Force Retries" narrative="The number of item forced retries counted, zero if they were not counted" stage="Force Retries"/>
      <output type="number" name="Total Count" narrative="The total number queue item operations counted" stage="Total Count"/>
      <output type="collection" name="Included Queues" narrative="The queues that were included in the report. Contains a single text column called 'Queue Name'." stage="Included Queues"/>
    </outputs>
    <onsuccess>6291c9da-172a-410b-bb84-f2ac2413c294</onsuccess>

  <stage stageid="37817cd3-49a5-41d7-9243-b5c101dbf066" name="Get Transactional Data" type="Action">
    <subsheetid>31c441e5-a950-4cbc-8527-3d935e019f7c</subsheetid>
    <narrative>
    </narrative>
    <displayx>390</displayx>
    <displayy>45</displayy>
    <displaywidth>120</displaywidth>
    <displayheight>30</displayheight>
    <font family="Tahoma" size="10" style="Regular" color="000000"/>
    <inputs>
      <input type="datetime" name="Start Date/Time" narrative="The UTC date/time from which activity counts should be retrieved. This is inclusive" expr="[Start Date]"/>
      <input type="datetime" name="End Date/Time" narrative="The UTC date/time up to and including which activity counts should be retrieved. This is inclusive. If empty, this will take all activity counts up until now." expr=""/>
      <input type="flag" name="Count item creations" narrative="True to count the work queue items being created - default is False" expr="False"/>
      <input type="flag" name="Count item locks" narrative="True to count the work queue items being locked - default is False" expr=""/>
      <input type="flag" name="Count item deferrals" narrative="True to count the work queue items being deferred - default is False" expr=""/>
      <input type="flag" name="Count item completions" narrative="True to count the work queue items being completed successfully - default is False" expr="False"/>
      <input type="flag" name="Count item exceptions with automatic retry" narrative="True to count the work queue items being marked with an exception and automatically retried - default is False" expr=""/>
      <input type="flag" name="Count item exceptions without automatic retry" narrative="True to count the work queue items being marked with an exception and without an automatic retry being create - default is False" expr=""/>
      <input type="flag" name="Count item deletions" narrative="True to count the work queue items being deleted - default is False" expr="False"/>
      <input type="flag" name="Count item forced retries" narrative="True to count the work queue items which were force retried - ie. they had been marked with an exception with no automatic retry, and had later been manually retried" expr=""/>
      <input type="collection" name="Excluded Queue Names" narrative="The names of the queues to retrieve the activity counts for. The names should be in a column within the collection named 'Queue Name'. If any queue names do not match a queue on the system, they are ignored." expr="[Excluded Queues]"/>
    </inputs>
    <outputs>
      <output type="number" name="Created" narrative="The number of item creations counted, zero if they were not counted" stage="Created"/>
      <output type="number" name="Locked" narrative="The number of item locks counted, zero if they were not counted" stage="Locked"/>
      <output type="number" name="Deferred" narrative="The number of defferals counted, zero if they were not counted" stage="Deferred"/>
      <output type="number" name="Completed" narrative="The number of item completions counted, zero if they were not counted" stage="Completed"/>
      <output type="number" name="Exceptions with retry" narrative="The number of item exceptions with automatic retry counted, zero if they were not counted" stage="Exceptions with retry"/>
      <output type="number" name="Exceptions with no retry" narrative="The number of item exceptions without automatic retry counted, zero if they were not counted" stage="Exceptions with no retry"/>
      <output type="number" name="Deletions" narrative="The number of item deletions counted, zero if they were not counted" stage="Deletions"/>
      <output type="number" name="Force Retries" narrative="The number of item forced retries counted, zero if they were not counted" stage="Force Retries"/>
      <output type="number" name="Total Count" narrative="The total number queue item operations counted" stage="Total Count"/>
      <output type="collection" name="Included Queues" narrative="The queues that were included in the report. Contains a single text column called 'Queue Name'." stage="Included Queues"/>
    </outputs>
    <onsuccess>81f84aad-df18-4179-b388-49470ee0d832</onsuccess>
    <resource object="Blueprism.Automate.clsWorkQueuesActions" action="Get Transaction Data"/>

Bug 4810 prevents the same password data item being assigned with "text" more than once, but this is not the point of this test.
